Introduction

Cha Eun Woo is a South Korean singer and actor under Fantagio Music. He is a member of the boy group ASTRO and a former member of the project group S.O.U.L.

Eunwoo debuted as a member of ASTRO on February 23, 2016 with the album "Spring Up".

He made his acting debut in 2014 in the drama "Modern Farmer". He also starred as the main lead in dramas such as "My ID is Gangnam Beauty", "Rookie Historian Goo Hae Ryung", "True Beauty", "Island","Wonderful World" and " A Good Day to be a Dog ".
